title: Is Alleged Capitol Rioter Kevin Seefried a ‘Registered Democrat and Biden Supporter’?
subtitle: Seefried was photographed brandishing a Confederate flag inside the halls of Congress. Claims that he is a secret Biden supporter are sorely lacking in evidence.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Kevin Seefried, who carried a Confederate flag into the U.S. Capitol during the attack on the building in January 2021, is registered as a Democrat in Delaware.
